  m_Name: Death - After Nova Point
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  data:
    convoName: Death - After Nova Point
    lines:
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: "I didn\u2019t think I would see you again.  "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Death
      expression: 
      line: 'You have much to learn. '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: 'Why do you return? '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Death
      expression: 
      line: 'I should be asking you the same. You stopped IRIS, and yet you still
        returned to this time. Why? Why not live out your dream as you had wanted? '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: "\u2026 "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: "I did what you asked of me. I traveled back in time and relived my \u2018atrocities.\u2019
        I saw life through the eyes of the spirits I encountered. I killed IRIS,
        mended my greatest error. "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Death
      expression: 
      line: 'And do you feel better now? Do you feel accomplished? '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: "I... No. I do not. The world was \u2026 different than I remembered. "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Death
      expression: 
      line: 'The world was terrible. People suffered everyday, and it went unnoticed
        by you. Nothing was different when you went back, you were simply shown how
        things really were. I ask again: do you feel better now? Better, having experienced
        the pain you caused society? '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: 'What was the point of this? '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Death
      expression: 
      line: "\u2026 "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Death
      expression: 
      line: "The door to your second greatest mistake has been opened for you. Shigora.
        The people whose deaths you caused, the clan you massacred. Noboru\u2013 "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: 'Noboru was a necessary sacrifice. '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Death
      expression: 
      line: "Are there necessary sacrifices, Orion? Killing, while something you
        take lightly, is a truly serious matter. All living beings are born with
        potential, cutting that short is nothing less than an insult to existence
        itself. You, Orion, kill freely\u2013 "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: 'IRIS deserved what it got. '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Death
      expression: 
      line: 'Maybe it did. But did the lives that it took? Did they deserve to die
        to keep you alive? '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: "\u2026 I\u2019ll go back. "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Death
      expression: 
      line: "Good \u2026 Now go, and I hope you\u2019ll consider fixing your mistakes. "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: "We\u2019ll see."
      audio: {fileID: 0}
